Strategies to Reduce Latency of a System:


Caching : 
Server side 
Client side


Asynchronous Procssing - Handle non-critical tasks in the background to improve responsiveness.

Persistent Connections: Reuse existing connections instead of creating new ones for each request.



CDNs

Load balancing - to prevent hot-spot servers 


DB optimisations : 
Indexing
Sharding
partitioning
Denormalisations
Materialized views
query optimisations





